WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:02.534
.

00:02.536 --> 00:06.672
- I'm not internal affairs.

00:06.674 --> 00:08.140
- If I find out different...

00:08.141 --> 00:10.175
You'll wish you never
set foot in the 21st.

00:10.177 --> 00:12.211
- This is complete horse--
- [whistles]

00:12.213 --> 00:14.546
Gotta get your hips into it--
like this.

00:14.548 --> 00:16.515
- This'll only take a minute.

00:19.086 --> 00:21.520
- I don't know what
you're talking about.

00:21.522 --> 00:23.255
- Your son is a pedophile
and a killer!

00:23.257 --> 00:24.590
- Leave!

00:24.592 --> 00:26.558
- Jay. I'm your partner.
- Yeah.

00:26.560 --> 00:28.327
- Talk to me.
- You don't wanna know.

00:28.329 --> 00:30.295
- Halstead, my office.

00:30.297 --> 00:31.563
I told you to let
the rodiger thing go.

00:31.565 --> 00:34.066
- I think lonnie's gonna
kill another kid.

00:34.068 --> 00:36.535
- You got eyes on you.
I've warned you all I can.

00:40.306 --> 00:41.640
- Yo!

00:41.642 --> 00:43.609
Did you guys catch the game
last night?

00:43.611 --> 00:46.245
18 seconds into overtime,
kane scores the backhander.

00:46.247 --> 00:50.149
Guy's on fire this season.

00:50.151 --> 00:52.684
What's with you two?
- Halstead.

00:57.357 --> 00:58.424
- Commander.

00:58.426 --> 01:02.061
- Halstead.
Have a seat.

01:02.063 --> 01:04.163
- I'll stand.

01:04.165 --> 01:06.198
- All right, after shift
last night, where were you?

01:06.200 --> 01:09.802
- Home.
Why?

01:09.804 --> 01:11.336
- So you're telling us

01:11.338 --> 01:12.571
You didn't go out at all
last night?

01:12.573 --> 01:14.573
- I'm telling you that
I watched the hawks game

01:14.575 --> 01:16.442
And I was in bed by midnight.

01:23.616 --> 01:28.854
- This was taken last night
near broadview and cicero.

01:28.856 --> 01:32.357
The car's registered
to lonnie rodiger.

01:32.359 --> 01:36.261
And that's you...

01:36.263 --> 01:39.565
Two cars behind.

01:39.567 --> 01:42.234
- Okay, so I happened
to be driving home

01:42.236 --> 01:44.837
Behind a pedophile.

01:44.839 --> 01:48.807
- Well, your alleged pedophile
was found dead this morning,

01:48.809 --> 01:51.176
Lafollette park.

01:51.178 --> 01:52.711
- What?

01:52.713 --> 01:56.381
- Someone tied a cord
around his neck.

01:59.719 --> 02:01.820
- So I hope you have
a better alibi

02:01.822 --> 02:03.255
Than watching
a hockey game...

02:03.257 --> 02:06.191
Alone.

02:06.193 --> 02:08.293
- Until this is
straightened out,

02:08.294 --> 02:10.362
You're officially stripped.

02:11.698 --> 02:13.899
- So expect a call
from internal affairs.

02:13.901 --> 02:15.567
They're going to want
to interview you

02:15.569 --> 02:18.237
As soon as possible.

02:18.239 --> 02:20.239
- You mean an interrogation.

02:20.241 --> 02:23.375
- You know
how this works, son.

02:28.648 --> 02:30.315
- Jay.

02:30.317 --> 02:32.151
- I'm the one who tried
to stop that freak.

02:32.153 --> 02:33.485
Now I'm the target.
- I know.

02:33.487 --> 02:35.287
Take this.
It's the number for dan hanes.

02:35.289 --> 02:37.289
He's the best police union rep
there is.

02:37.291 --> 02:38.790
You call him...

02:38.792 --> 02:41.860
And then you tell me
how you want to handle this.

02:41.862 --> 02:45.164
- This is unbelievable.

02:45.166 --> 02:48.867
Hey, jin, I need
the rodiger homicide file.

02:48.869 --> 02:51.737
- As a suspect in his murder,
that's highly unauthorized.

02:51.739 --> 02:53.338
- Come on, man!
- We're done!

02:53.340 --> 02:55.774
I'm back to manning
traffic patterns

02:55.776 --> 02:57.843
For streets and san.

02:57.845 --> 02:59.845
- Told you to be careful,
didn't I?

02:59.847 --> 03:01.380
- I just got suspended.

03:01.382 --> 03:02.614
- You're shocked?

03:02.616 --> 03:04.650
I'm the one who brought you
into this unit.

03:04.652 --> 03:06.385
- Tony, this wasn't me.

03:06.387 --> 03:07.753
- I got to clock in.

03:07.755 --> 03:09.655
Go get yourself a lawyer
right now

03:09.657 --> 03:11.423
And keep your mouth shut.

03:15.595 --> 03:17.529
[siren approaching,
indistinct chatter]

03:17.531 --> 03:20.432
- He--he came out of nowhere,
I swear.

03:20.434 --> 03:22.534
I didn't see him.
- I understand, ma'am,

03:22.536 --> 03:24.436
But we need you
to get out of the way

03:24.438 --> 03:26.872
So these men can do their jobs,
okay?

03:26.874 --> 03:28.473
[radio chatter]

03:28.475 --> 03:30.409
- Old lady plows her boat
through an intersection,

03:30.411 --> 03:32.744
And she's the only one
without a scratch.

03:34.214 --> 03:35.581
- Hey, sit tight.

03:35.583 --> 03:37.382
We're going
to get you out of there.

03:42.522 --> 03:43.689
- Okay!

03:43.691 --> 03:46.525
More!

03:46.527 --> 03:48.260
Hold it!

03:50.530 --> 03:52.631
[low chatter]

03:58.972 --> 04:01.473
- Hey! The driver of this car,
he decked my guy!

04:01.475 --> 04:02.874
- You ungrateful prick!

04:02.876 --> 04:04.776
- You all right?
- Yeah.

04:04.778 --> 04:06.778
- It wasn't his fault.
Why'd he run?

04:06.780 --> 04:09.448
- Check the car.

04:16.723 --> 04:19.257
- Hey!
What you got for this?

04:19.260 --> 04:21.793
- [grunting]

04:23.596 --> 04:25.664
- Damn.

04:33.973 --> 04:37.676
- No wonder
he was in such a hurry.

04:37.678 --> 04:46.451
.

04:46.453 --> 04:49.755
- Well, it's evidence
in a murder case,

04:49.757 --> 04:51.556
So it could be impounded
for a while.

04:51.558 --> 04:53.558
- Well, my insurance isn't going
to cover a loaner.

04:53.560 --> 04:55.494
Will the cpd
provide me with one?

04:55.496 --> 04:58.430
Go ahead and pick one out
from the lot.

04:58.432 --> 05:00.632
Go talk to sergeant platt,
front desk.

05:00.634 --> 05:03.468
She'll give you
the keys, okay?

05:03.470 --> 05:04.870
The owner
of the car's clean.

05:04.872 --> 05:06.772
The car was reported stolen
from a parking garage

05:06.774 --> 05:08.373
About a week ago.

05:08.375 --> 05:09.975
- Hey, the torso recovered
from the trunk

05:09.977 --> 05:11.510
Had an artificial hip,

05:11.512 --> 05:13.445
So I asked jin to trace
the serial number

05:13.447 --> 05:16.982
- Doing it that way's actually
faster than a dna test.

05:16.984 --> 05:19.084
Only takes me a couple hours
instead of a couple weeks.

05:19.086 --> 05:20.952
- It's a good thing you're back
to doing your day job

05:20.954 --> 05:25.357
Instead of personal favors.

05:25.359 --> 05:27.592
Keep hitting the bushes.

05:29.462 --> 05:33.532
- Hey, so you think halstead
did it or what?

05:33.534 --> 05:34.966
Lindsay, come on,
it's a question.

05:34.968 --> 05:36.468
You never know around here
sometimes.

05:36.470 --> 05:38.537
- What's that supposed to mean?

05:38.539 --> 05:40.706
- Nothing.

05:43.776 --> 05:46.912
- To be honest,
I don't feel any sympathy.

05:46.914 --> 05:49.481
- Do the police have any idea
who did it?

05:49.483 --> 05:53.819
- We're still trying
to piece that together.

05:53.821 --> 05:55.454
Gail, do you have any milk
for this?

05:55.456 --> 05:57.022
- Oh, yeah.
- Thank you.

05:57.024 --> 05:59.591
Sorry.
- I'm sorry.

06:05.698 --> 06:08.367
They suspended me.

06:08.369 --> 06:10.068
They think I did it.

06:10.070 --> 06:14.005
So if you did something...

06:14.007 --> 06:16.541
Then tell me now,

06:16.543 --> 06:20.412
And we'll figure this out
together.

06:20.414 --> 06:22.914
- Jay, I have been fantasizing
about it for years,

06:22.916 --> 06:25.117
But I didn't do it.

06:25.119 --> 06:27.753
After all you've done
for this family,

06:27.755 --> 06:30.622
If you need me to confess...

06:30.624 --> 06:32.491
I will.

