06:41.634 --> 06:43.769
- Hey!
He's dead because of you!

06:43.771 --> 06:44.936
- Oh, man.

06:44.938 --> 06:46.405
- None of this
would have happened

06:46.407 --> 06:50.475
- Lonnie brought this on himself
and you know it.

06:56.816 --> 06:59.184
- You're a man short.

07:01.053 --> 07:03.622
- Halstead's under investigation
for murder.

07:03.624 --> 07:04.756
You want to cash in on that?

07:04.758 --> 07:06.725
- I deserve to be
in intelligence.

07:06.727 --> 07:08.960
An opportunity
is an opportunity.

07:08.962 --> 07:10.162
[knocking on door]

07:10.164 --> 07:12.764
- I got a match
on the artificial hip.

07:12.766 --> 07:15.434
Dr. Richard elliot...
The dna consultant

07:15.436 --> 07:17.536
Who testified
for the state's attorney.

07:17.538 --> 07:18.670
- Yeah, I knew him.

07:18.672 --> 07:20.472
Helped put away
some major hitters.

07:20.474 --> 07:23.175
- Well, his wife filed a missing
persons report on him yesterday.

07:23.177 --> 07:26.611
- Nice work.

07:28.881 --> 07:33.518
Let's take a ride.

07:33.520 --> 07:34.820
- He left his office
two nights ago,

07:34.822 --> 07:36.621
And he never came home.

07:36.623 --> 07:38.190
He called me when he got
on lakeshore drive,

07:38.192 --> 07:41.126
But then he never answered
his phone after that.

07:41.128 --> 07:43.128
- As a consultant
for the prosecution,

07:43.130 --> 07:45.130
I assume
he's gotten death threats.

07:45.132 --> 07:48.500
- He's testified in hundreds
of dna cases.

07:48.502 --> 07:50.936
I told him
I wanted him to retire,

07:50.938 --> 07:55.006
To go back to teaching,
but he loved his work.

07:55.008 --> 07:58.176
- Was he about to testify
in any upcoming trials?

08:08.588 --> 08:10.622
- The trial was supposed
to start tomorrow.

08:10.624 --> 08:15.827
- This clown, nicholas djurovic,
aka nick the dj.

08:15.829 --> 08:18.230
- Ma'am, we're going to need you
to go downtown

08:18.232 --> 08:21.666
With the patrolman to...
Deal with the remains.

08:23.903 --> 08:28.540
- [sobbing]

08:28.542 --> 08:30.575
- "the remains," huh?

08:32.645 --> 08:35.113
Alvin, I want you
to do a drive-by.

08:35.115 --> 08:36.982
- Yeah, just shoot me the name
and I'll suit up.

08:36.984 --> 08:40.719
So you'll let me know
what's going on with halstead?

08:40.721 --> 08:43.154
- I told him not to pursue
his vendetta.

08:43.155 --> 08:46.091
- So we're just gonna to let
this kid twist in the wind?

08:46.093 --> 08:47.959
- He created this problem.

08:47.961 --> 08:49.561
He can't figure his way
out of it,

08:49.563 --> 08:51.596
He doesn't belong
in our unit anyways.

08:51.598 --> 08:54.032
- All right.

08:55.969 --> 08:59.604
He got jammed up on
an aggravated assault charge--

08:59.606 --> 09:01.640
- I want your opinion,
I'll ask.

09:07.213 --> 09:09.948
[muffled electronica]

09:09.950 --> 09:13.785
- Djurovic, this is cpd!

09:13.787 --> 09:15.554
- Chicago pd!

09:15.556 --> 09:18.223
Woman: Oh!

09:21.561 --> 09:24.195
[thumping electronica]

09:24.197 --> 09:25.330
- Clear!
- Clear!

09:25.332 --> 09:33.939
